::Feline::

She looked at the other bots who were in the mess hall.  She smiled a 
pleasing smile at them and turned to face Zardus. She took the tip of 
her tail and softly brushed it against the back of his neck.  She 
smiled and purred. She wanted the other bots to see 
her 'affectionate' nature.  She knew the power a female could hold 
over a male.  And she was going to use it to the fullest. Per her 
programming, she couldn't betray her leader, but being second in 
command was on her mind.  
She took the tip of her index finger and gently traced his spine, 
from the top of the neck down to the lower back. Then she brought her 
hand back to rest on her hip.  She leaned forward and purred softly 
into his ear.  
Then she then went over and sat down at a table near the other bots.  
She smiled sweetly at them, crossed her legs and waited for Zardus to 
bring her a drink.  She let her tail rest on top of her thighs and 
twitched the end of her tail.
